did.unittitle: Election Returns of Allegheny County, Pa. Records
did.abstract: This collection includes the official return books for the general, municipal, and primary elections in Pittsburgh, Clairton, McKeesport, Duquesne, and other townships, boroughs, and school districts of Allegheny County, Pa., 1926-1983.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Notes
scopecontent.p: This collection includes four series. Series I and II contain the official return books for the general, municipal, and primary elections in Pittsburgh, Clairton, McKeesport, Duquesne, and other townships, boroughs, and school districts of Allegheny County, Pa., 1926-1983, not including the years 1937-1940.

National Election records include President. State election records include United States Senator, Governor, Lieutenant Governor, Secretary of Internal Affairs, Supreme Court Judge, Judge of Superior Court, Representatives in Congress, Senator in the General Assembly, and Representative in the General Assembly. Municipal election records include County Controller, Clerk of Courts, District Attorney, Director of the Poor, Judge of the Supreme Court, Judge of the Court of Common Pleas, County Treasurer, County Commissioner, Recorder of Deeds, Register of Wills and Ex Officio Clerk of The Orphans Clerk, Prothonotary, and Judges of County Court.

Series III consists of tabulations and summaries of primary and general elections from various years from 1939 to 1979. Series IV contains voter registration statistics, 1977-1983. All series are arranged by date.
Note: This collection was acquired in four parts, or accessions, and is divided into series according to the date it was acquired. The majority of these records have been microfilmed.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Notes
scopecontent.p: Series I includes microfilmed records of election returns, 1926-1936. These records are part of the original accession, 1965.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Notes
scopecontent.p: Series II contains microfilmed election returns, 1941-1969. These records were part of the 1970 accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Notes
scopecontent.p: Series III consists of tabulations and summaries of primary and general elections from various years from 1939 to 1979.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Notes
scopecontent.p: Series IV contains voter registration statistics, 1977-1983.
